echo '$ json -d '\''{"type":"dict","args":[{"name":"foo","type":"boolean"},{"name":"bar","type":"number"},{"name":"baz","type":"string"},{"name":"faa","type":"object"}]}'\'' <<< '\''{"bar":1,"baz":"","foo":false}'\'''
